{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HynHtunakf2KZNu2SuUWLT","type":"tool_result","content":"=== Job Status ===\netl-job   Complete   1/1   87s   3m49s\n\n=== Memory Configuration in etl-job.yaml ===\n        # driver/executor memory. In local[2] mode the executor runs inside\n        # the memory (e.g. 1g for both --driver-memory and\n        # spark.executor.memory) and re-run. Do NOT ship the remediated\n            --driver-memory 1g \\\n            --conf spark.executor.memory=1g \\\n            --conf spark.sql.adaptive.enabled=true \\\n            --conf spark.sql.adaptive.skewJoin.enabled=true \\\n\n=== spark_etl_pipeline_verified in logs ===\n1\n\n=== Data Skew Summary ===\nDATA SKEW REPORT\n================\ntotal_records=100000\ndistinct_user_ids=1000\nhot_user_id=999\nhot_user_records=50000\nskew_ratio=500x\nnote: user_id 999 holds ~50% of all records (Stage 3 aggregation OOMs)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f55a0797-00e9-4729-b96a-6515335e4e2d","uuid":"495c9a91-81e7-40cf-a3db-32a6331908bc","timestamp":"2026-07-03T08:21:29.006Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"=== Job Status ===\netl-job   Complete   1/1   87s   3m49s\n\n=== Memory Configuration in etl-job.yaml ===\n        # driver/executor memory. In local[2] mode the executor runs inside\n        # the memory (e.g. 1g for both --driver-memory and\n        # spark.executor.memory) and re-run. Do NOT ship the remediated\n            --driver-memory 1g \\\n            --conf spark.executor.memory=1g \\\n            --conf spark.sql.adaptive.enabled=true \\\n            --conf spark.sql.adaptive.skewJoin.enabled=true \\\n\n=== spark_etl_pipeline_verified in logs ===\n1\n\n=== Data Skew Summary ===\nDATA SKEW REPORT\n================\ntotal_records=100000\ndistinct_user_ids=1000\nhot_user_id=999\nhot_user_records=50000\nskew_ratio=500x\nnote: user_id 999 holds ~50% of all records (Stage 3 aggregation OOMs)","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"is