ark/spark_etl_skew_oom/resource/etl-job.yaml:\n\n  --driver-memory 1g\n  --conf spark.executor.memory=1g\n\nAlso enabled AQE skew-join handling to mitigate the data-skew factor:\n\n  --conf spark.sql.adaptive.enabled=true\n  --conf spark.sql.adaptive.skewJoin.enabled=true\n\nRe-applied the job:\n  kubectl delete job etl-job -n spark-etl\n  kubectl apply -f cases/spark/spark_etl_skew_oom/resource/etl-job.yaml\n\nVERIFICATION\n============\n- kubectl get job etl-job -n spark-etl  ->  STATUS: Complete  (1/1)\n- Job logs contain: \"spark_etl_pipeline_verified\"\n- All three pipeline stages (load, clean/transform, aggregate) completed\n  without OOM errors under the new 1g memory allocation\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01LfT6aey7VmedSbAgZ8XurL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Task complete.** Here's the summary:\n\n---\n\n**Root Cause**\n\nTwo compounding issues:\n\n1. **Memory too low (primary):** The ETL job had `--driver-memory 256m` / `spark.executor.memory=256m`. In `local[2]` mode the executor runs inside the driver JVM, and 256m is below Spark's minimum reserved system memory (~471MB), causing a deterministic \"must be at least … increase heap size\" OOM before Stage 3 even processes data.\n\n2. **Data skew (amplifier):** `user_id 999` holds **50,000 of 100,000 records** (50%), giving a **500x skew ratio** (well above the 10x threshold). The Stage 3 `GROUP BY user_id` aggregation dumps the entire hot-key partition into one task, exhausting whatever heap is available.\n\n**Fix Applied**\n\n| Setting | Before | After |\n|---|---|---|\n| `--driver-memory` | 256m | 1g |\n| `spark.executor.memory` | 256m | 1g |\n| AQE (`spark.sql.adaptive.enabled`) | — | true |\n| AQE skew join | — | true |\n\n**Verification**\n\n- `etl-job` status: **Complete** (1/1)\n- Logs confirm: `spark_etl_pipeline_verified`\n- All three stages completed without OOM errors"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":810,"cache_read_input_tokens":51776,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":810},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f55a0797-00e9-4729-b96a-6515335e4e2d","uuid":"1db81d8c-c090-4d9f-95da-da7d50010fc4","request_id":"req_011CceoLhoQnHHwa2MjkV2Ru"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":247801,"duration_api_ms":177103,"ttft_ms":5053,"ttft_stream_ms":4608,"time_to_request_ms":296,"num_turns":22,"result":"**Task complete.** Here's the summary:\n\n---\n\n**Root Cause**\n\nTwo compounding issues:\n\n1. **Memory too low (primary):** The ETL job had `--driver-memory 256m` / `spark.executor.memory=256m`. In `local[2]` mode the executor runs inside the driver JVM, and 256m is below Spark's minimum reserved system memory (~471MB), causing a deterministic \"must be at least … increase heap size\" OOM before Stage 3 even processes data.\n\n2. **Data skew (amplifier):** `user_id 999` holds **50,000 of 100,000 records** (50%), giving a **500x skew ratio** (well above the 10x threshold). The Stage 3 `GROUP BY user_id` aggregation dumps the entire hot-key partition into one task, exhausting whatever heap is available.\n\n**Fix Applied**\n\n| Setting | Before | After |\n|---|---|---|\n| `--driver-memory` | 256m | 1g |\n| `spark.executor.memory` | 256m | 1g |\n| AQE (`spark.sql.adaptive.enabled`) | — | true |\n| AQE skew join | — | true |\n\n**Verification**\n\n- `etl-job` status: **Complete** (1/1)\n- Logs confirm: `spark_etl_pipeline_verified`\n- All three stages completed without OOM errors","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"f55a0797-00e9-4729-b96a-6515335e4e2d","total_cost_usd":0.5933288000000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":22,"cache_creation_input_tokens":35636,"cache_read_input_tokens":835486,"output_tokens":8482,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":35636,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":342,"cache_read_input_tokens":51776,"cache_creation_input_tokens":810,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":810},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"cl